š·Ã]<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";a:14:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1396";s:4:"name";s:11:"Access Bars";s:4:"slug";s:11:"access-bars";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1396";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:508:"Access Bars are 32 points on oneâ€™s head which when gently touched, release anything that doesnâ€™t allow one to receive. These points have the storage of all the thoughts, beliefs, ideas, and emotions that one has stored in any lifetime. Each Access Bar session is capable of releasing 5-10 thousand years of limitations corresponding with the specific bar being touched. This is a nurturing and relaxing process where one can let go of any barriers and be willing to change in all aspects of oneâ€™s life.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"70";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1420";s:4:"name";s:13:"Angel Reading";s:4:"slug";s:13:"angel-reading";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1420";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:285:"Angel Reading is a non-denominational spiritual healing method that involves working with a personâ€™s guardian angels and archangels to heal and harmonize every aspect of their life. Angel therapy also helps one to receive the divine guidance more clearly from the Creator and angels.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:2:"53";}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1535";s:4:"name";s:10:"Breathwork";s:4:"slug";s:10:"breathwork";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1535";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:231:"These are unique and powerful conscious breathing techniques that aid in releasing the birth trauma and other limiting traumas encoded in all levels of our cells. Breathwork helps release physical and emotional toxins from the root";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:2:"10";}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1527";s:4:"name";s:34:"Energetic Analysis and Corrections";s:4:"slug";s:34:"energetic-analysis-and-corrections";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1527";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1502";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1391";s:4:"name";s:14:"Energy Healing";s:4:"slug";s:14:"energy-healing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1391";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:314:"The human body holds energy centers which can lead to dis-ease when imbalanced. Energy Healing is a method of channeling healing energy into those centers to restore balance. There are many therapies that use Energy Healing, and can be hands-on, hands-off and distant (where the patient is in a different location)";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1550";s:4:"name";s:20:"Family Constellation";s:4:"slug";s:20:"family-constellation";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1550";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:486:"Family Constellation (Trans-generational Healing) is a dynamic therapy to heal an individual from deep underlying family patterns and trauma within their family system. This process involves taking the individualâ€™s issues into a group with the therapist, where others in the group play roles of his/her family members. This process taps into the underlying energy dynamics of the family constellation, thereby opening up new possibilities and improving the relationships dramatically.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"26";}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1447";s:4:"name";s:13:"Hypno Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:12:"hypnotherapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1447";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:360:"The mind, when taken to a hypnotic state through deep but conscious relaxation, can be guided to overcome past trauma, addictions, health conditions and self-limiting behaviours. It helps peel away the layers where our deepest blocks and memories are sub-consciously buried. There are many forms of hypnotherapy, all proved to be effective on different levels.";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:2:"11";}i:7;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1548";s:4:"name";s:19:"Inner Child Healing";s:4:"slug";s:19:"inner-child-healing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1548";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:593:"Inner Child Work offers a thorough understanding and healing of the child within oneself and opens the floodgates to the bounty of inner being. If there was an overt abuse or neglect in oneâ€™s childhood or more subtle pressures and expectations, their psyche continues to bear childhood wounds. Everything one has ever experienced is stored in the body and mind. Events from childhood remain unhealed in most and become major contributors to the conflicts and problems experienced as adults. Inner child work shows how to give oneâ€™s Inner Child the nurturing attention it has always needed.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"46";}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1423";s:4:"name";s:10:"Numerology";s:4:"slug";s:10:"numerology";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1423";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:600:"According to Numerology, the Universe speaks in the language of numbers that it is not random but one that works through a mathematical approach. Numerologists also believe that each one of us has three numbers that are the most relevant: Psychic Number, Destiny Number and Name Number. They are well-versed in this ancient study which includes the analysis of numbers, patterns, their invisible influence, energetic relevance and their significance in our lives. Numerologists often suggest methods to alter these numbers to help us get rid of karmic blocks and throw open a flow of positive energy.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:2:"53";}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1448";s:4:"name";s:20:"Past Life Regression";s:4:"slug";s:20:"past-life-regression";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1448";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:738:"Past Life Regression is based on the belief that we carry the memory of all of our lives and experiences deep within our psyches/causal bodies. By using hypnotherapy, the therapist helps the patient to delve deep into their psyche and access past memories from other reincarnations that still affect the individual at a subconscious level. Once this information has been received, the therapist can help the patient complete the healing, at both conscious and subconscious levels.

<strong>It can solve:</strong> Trauma,Panic Attack,Fear &amp; Beleifs in destructive dark energies ,Birth Trauma,Post Traumatic Stress Disorder,Suicidal Tendancies ,Trauma of Sudden Death,Trauma of Sexual Abuse,Phobia ,Addiction issue,Clinical Depression";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1447";s:5:"count";s:3:"103";}i:10;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1536";s:4:"name";s:10:"Rebirthing";s:4:"slug";s:10:"rebirthing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1536";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:451:"Rebirthing is a gentle yet conscious breathing technique that not only brings into conscious awareness the unconsciously held beliefs and emotions but also the relationships we have with our bodies, ourselves and our intimates. On practicing this conscious breathing, it becomes possible to resolve, integrate and heal previously unresolved issues within ourselves, filling us with more joy and allowing us to reach our true potential as human beings.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1535";s:5:"count";s:2:"25";}i:11;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1392";s:4:"name";s:5:"Reiki";s:4:"slug";s:5:"reiki";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1392";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:526:"Reiki is an ancient Japanese form of energy healing where the practitioner channelizes Chi energy from the Universal Life Force through their hands to a person, place, event, relationship or even a long-distance occurrence. Reiki is also used for chakra healing, chakra balancing, healing chronic ailments, removing energetic blocks and cleansing the auric field. This extra energy infused with the astral body kick-starts the innate ability of the body to heal itself, rejuvenates the flow of Chi and clears emotional blocks.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:3:"142";}i:12;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1528";s:4:"name";s:24:"SE -5 1000 Scalar Energy";s:4:"slug";s:23:"se-5-1000-scalar-energy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1528";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:403:"SE-5 1000 is a product of Subtle Energy Research based on the concepts of Radionics and Biofield theory where SE-5 works through the IDFs (Intrinsic Data Field) that contain biofield information, like a microfilm, about how energy is organized and structured into matter. The SE-5 is designed to detect and balance these biofields with precision and accuracy through the use of Scalar Energy vibrations.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1527";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";}i:13;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1421";s:4:"name";s:18:"Tarot Card Reading";s:4:"slug";s:18:"tarot-card-reading";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1421";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:472:"In Tarot Card Reading, the therapist uses a pack of picture cards for the individual to choose from.By this method the Tarot Card Reader is able to connect with the present moment to tap into the inner source of all beings. The Reader studies the combination of cards picked by the individual and interprets the messages through their knowledge of symbolism and intuition. This guidance is the language of the Universe with specific relevance to the life of an individual.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:3:"126";}}}